text: Cagalah Yallaa kee kay farmoytah Qeebih ugteeh Baaxô bagul Sinam Qidimiiy maali Seelabut Baaxó baysa marih galto ken Qidee kee hinnay Qiddi ken heenih caxxat ken xinkiyeenih ken fannisee kee hinnay gaboobii kee ibitte ittal Hoxak migdi gabaa kee guri iba keenik Argaquk, hinnay baaxok ken xiiriyi, hinnay ken baaxol elle casbit ken hayi yakkeenimi, toh keenik addunyal xixxibisiyyaay wacarriysiyya, usun akeeral kaxxa digaala-lon
